==Useful Info==
'''Fire crabs''' are fairly durable crustaceans with fiery melee attacks and the ability to flood their surroundings with [[cloud]]s of flame. Fortunately, they are only found in the deeper sections of [[the Dungeon]], [[the Depths]], and [[the Vaults]]. You can also find them in a volcano-themed [[Lair]] end-vault and in actual [[volcano]]es, wading through lava.

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*[[Fire resistance]] can significantly reduce their damage output.
*Don't expect running away to do you much good. Even if you can escape the clouds in a step, they'll be likely to blast you with new clouds. Kill them quick to take the fire out at the source!
*They have moderately low willpower. [[Wand]]s can work at disabling them, though it may take a few tries.
*They are vulnerable to [[poison]], so poison in general is effective. Waiting for poison to tick down can be dangerous without rF+, however.

==History==
*Fire crabs can travel through [[lava]] since [[0.31]].
